@startuml state-event-lifecycle

skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam pageMargin 10

title Integration Event Lifecycle

[*] --> Created : Domain operation\ncompletes

Created : EventId = NewGuid()
Created : CreatedAt = UtcNow

Created --> Serialized : IMessageSerializer\n.Serialize<TEvent>()

Serialized : Wrapped in\nMessageEnvelope

Serialized --> Published : RedisMessageBus\n.PublishAsync()

Published : Sent to Redis\nPub/Sub channel

Published --> Delivered : Redis delivers\nto subscribers

Delivered : Subscriber receives\nbyte[] message

Delivered --> Handled : IIntegrationEventHandler\n.HandleAsync()

Handled : Domain side-effects\napplied

Handled --> [*]

Published --> Failed : Redis unavailable\nor serialization error
Failed --> [*]

@enduml
